as
Homonym Number:
Word Class:adverb
Sense Number:
Definition:an intensifier in the construction '[adjective] + as' (elliptical for the full form of comparison, 'as [adjective] as [NP]'); initially in the phrase sweet as (q.v.), extended to other adjectives as illustrated below
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
